    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 104.</p><p>Tier I: Elite Skirmisher</p><p>Advantaged Strike. You have advantage on the first attack you make on your turn.</p><p>Deflection. As a reaction when you or a creature within range of your currently equipped melee weapon is targeted by an attack, you can attempt to deflect it. Make a weapon attack. If the result is higher than the triggering strike’s attack roll, the attack misses as you deflect it.</p></div>",
